Could be killers.

15:39.474 --> 15:40.606
(scoffs)
Really?

15:40.608 --> 15:42.972
You have a website and a YouTube
channel.

15:42.974 --> 15:45.341
How dangerous can you be?

15:45.973 --> 15:48.539
I will be many things.

15:48.541 --> 15:50.542
But boring will not be one of
them.

15:51.306 --> 15:53.439
Masks don't scare me.

15:53.441 --> 15:55.941
Oh, we all wear masks,
Allison.

15:56.708 --> 15:57.905
Even you.

15:57.907 --> 16:00.808
It's what's underneath that
scares us.

16:05.641 --> 16:07.640
(metallic knock)

16:11.506 --> 16:13.508
(keys tapping)

16:17.307 --> 16:19.870
(The Voice on recording)
What scares you, Allison?

16:19.872 --> 16:21.638
(Allison on recording)
I don't know if things scare me.

16:21.640 --> 16:24.471
(The Voice) Maybe I'm not being clear.
What limits you?

16:24.473 --> 16:26.475
