39:22.439 --> 39:23.872
(Red Skull)
Hello, Allison.

39:24.739 --> 39:25.904
Hi.

39:25.906 --> 39:28.840
(Red Skull) I just finished
watching your submission.

39:29.705 --> 39:31.672
I think you're an excellent
candidate.

39:32.872 --> 39:34.240
Really?

39:35.871 --> 39:36.771
That's great.

39:37.905 --> 39:39.937
(Red Skull)
I need a letter from your doctor

39:39.939 --> 39:41.940
stating you're in good mental
and physical condition.

39:43.005 --> 39:44.374
Can you do this?

39:44.972 --> 39:47.173
Yeah. That's no problem.

39:49.340 --> 39:51.339
(Red Skull)
What scares you, Allison?

39:54.340 --> 39:56.340
I don't know if things scare me.

39:56.806 --> 39:58.806
(Red Skull)
Maybe I'm not being clear.

39:59.805 --> 40:01.339
What limits you?

40:01.772 --> 40:04.270
What holds you back from living?

40:04.272 --> 40:06.274
(slow piano jazz music)

40:11.505 --> 40:14.636
