The dog's alive! Yeah!

42:58.938 --> 43:01.338
John Hainey, thirty-eight years
old.

43:02.239 --> 43:04.906
Been with Perdition for... geez.

43:05.438 --> 43:07.537
Going on ten years now.

43:07.539 --> 43:08.640
This is Russell.

43:10.973 --> 43:12.438
This is pretty boy, Floyd.

43:12.639 --> 43:13.504
Prop gun.

43:13.506 --> 43:15.673
I used to work in special makeup
effects.

43:15.973 --> 43:17.636
Underground films, mostly.

43:17.638 --> 43:18.706
(speaking Japanese)

43:19.672 --> 43:20.769
(translator)
You play how many characters?

43:20.771 --> 43:21.570
Three.

43:21.572 --> 43:24.240
Beanie, Psycho Clown, and
Gorilla.

43:24.906 --> 43:26.536
Now, the Gorilla is obviously
the one closest

43:26.538 --> 43:27.803
to my own personality.

43:27.805 --> 43:28.869
When I first started,

43:28.871 --> 43:30.536
I was what we call White Skull.

43:30.538 --> 43:31.903
That's the entry-level position.

43:31.905 --> 43:33.173
Mainly grunt work.

43:33.571 --> 43:34.603
But after a year of that,

43:34.605 --> 43:36.302
I graduated character work.

43:36.304 --> 43:37.971
This gives me more of an
opportunity

43:37.973 --> 43:39.540
to express myself artistically.

43:47.472 --> 43:48.806
(speaking Japanese)

43:49.238 --> 43:50.171
(translator)
Tell us your name.

43:50.173 --> 43:52.306
Phil Cutter. Been with Perdition
ten years.

43:53.372 --> 43:54.903
(translator) What made you
want to scare people?

43:54.905 --> 43:56.470
(Cutter)
I served eight tours,

43:56.472 --> 43:58.236
Iraq and Afghanistan,

43:58.238 --> 44:00.336
and uh saw some bad shit,

44:00.338 --> 44:02.173
and this is therapy for me.

44:04.571 --> 44:05.769
(translator)
How did you meet Bob?

44:05.771 --> 44:07.336
(Cutter)
He was a struggling screenwriter

44:07.338 --> 44:08.503
when I met him.

44:08.505 --> 44:09.937
He was writing a Vietnam script,

44:09.939 --> 44:11.971
something for a military
advisor.

44:11.973 --> 44:14.004
He was a friend of a friend so I
helped out.

44:14.006 --> 44:16.004
The script went nowhere, but uh

44:16.006 --> 44:18.269
