collaboration,

44:18.271 --> 44:20.672
and uh, he's an interesting guy.

44:24.005 --> 44:26.672
(translator) What unique
skills do you bring Perdition?

44:29.405 --> 44:31.406
(ominous slow electronic music)

45:31.705 --> 45:33.705
What do you want from us?

45:34.805 --> 45:36.805
What?

45:39.405 --> 45:41.004
Now listen carefully.

45:41.006 --> 45:42.569
It's a simple question.

45:42.571 --> 45:44.539
What do you

45:45.671 --> 45:46.739
want from us?

45:47.872 --> 45:49.873
I don't know what you mean.

46:03.872 --> 46:05.540
What do you

46:06.371 --> 46:07.506
want from us?

46:08.006 --> 46:10.539
I want you to push me to my
limits!

46:14.439 --> 46:15.540
(scoffs)

46:17.871 --> 46:19.172
(Allison whimpers)

46:49.605 --> 46:52.273
(Zachary) What are you-what are
you doing to her?

46:53.304 --> 46:54.604
What are you doing to her?!

46:54.606 --> 46:55.639
Stop!

46:59.405 --> 47:01.470
What do you want from us,
Allison?

47:01.472 --> 47:04.639
Stop! I want you to stop!

47:06.539 --> 47:08.506
