47:20.404 --> 47:22.004
What do you want from us,
Allison?

47:22.006 --> 47:23.839
I felt like I was drowning!

47:24.639 --> 47:25.940
You can't do this!

47:30.539 --> 47:31.837
(Zachary)
Stop it!

47:31.839 --> 47:33.903
Stop it, you're gonna kill her!

47:33.905 --> 47:35.172
