back to me,

48:25.672 --> 48:26.907
do you understand?

48:27.438 --> 48:29.337
Now listen, here we go, here we
go

48:29.339 --> 48:31.336
2, 5, 4,

48:31.338 --> 48:33.472
6, 0, 8, 9.

48:34.605 --> 48:36.670
Six, oh, eight.

48:36.672 --> 48:37.673
Yeah

48:38.672 --> 48:39.873
(speaking Japanese)

48:40.605 --> 48:41.904
(translator)
What's happening?

48:41.906 --> 48:43.337
(Red Skull)
Don't worry.

48:43.339 --> 48:44.969
It's all under control.

48:44.971 --> 48:47.772
It's okay. 6, 8, 4,

48:48.238 --> 48:50.238
1, 3, 7, 2.

48:50.671 --> 48:52.672
