6, 8, 5

48:53.271 --> 48:55.273
...no, 4, 4...

48:56.906 --> 48:59.173
Calm down, calm down. it's
okay.

48:59.805 --> 49:01.870
(crying)
one

49:01.872 --> 49:03.373
(soothing sounds)

49:04.338 --> 49:06.338
Take it easy. It's alright.

49:07.839 --> 49:08.905
It's alright.

49:17.439 --> 49:18.503
Stop. Stop!

49:18.505 --> 49:20.405
Let go of me! Help!

49:20.871 --> 49:22.505
Stop! Let go!

49:23.739 --> 49:24.740
