49:25.605 --> 49:28.203
Why'd you say "Daddy"?

49:27.239 --> 49:28.870
Because I'm fucked up, okay?

49:28.872 --> 49:30.873
Now we're getting somewhere.

49:31.971 --> 49:33.273
Why are you here?

49:33.738 --> 49:35.570
