49:47.605 --> 49:49.470
From my parents.

49:49.472 --> 49:51.604
Sounds like they know you pretty
well.

49:51.606 --> 49:52.939
What else they have to say?

49:53.904 --> 49:55.705
That I'm not strong enough.

49:55.938 --> 49:57.272
That I'm weak.

49:57.671 --> 49:58.872
I'm... I'm

49:59.471 --> 50:01.473
- (sobbing) a loser!
- Keep going!

50:01.938 --> 50:02.938
(Allison)
Hey!

50:03.672 --> 50:05.473
Oh, you ready to talk now?

50:06.372 --> 50:07.373
