52:39.771 --> 52:41.302
(White Skull)
Fuck!

52:41.304 --> 52:42.936
God, this mask can go fuck
itself,

52:42.938 --> 52:44.469
I'm tired of this thing.

52:44.471 --> 52:45.470
You know, I shoulda been

52:45.472 --> 52:46.473
fucking Peep Show Girl.

52:47.737 --> 52:48.935
I'm way hotter than that bitch

52:48.937 --> 52:50.637
anyway and then she just comes
in like,

52:50.639 --> 52:52.436
"I'm Hainey's wife!

52:52.438 --> 52:54.338
