53:10.404 --> 53:11.405
Look at me.

53:13.638 --> 53:14.804
Who's your sister?

53:18.606 --> 53:19.405
Who loves you?

53:23.472 --> 53:24.872
You bet your ass I do.

53:34.938 --> 53:37.473
We're gonna get outta here soon,
okay?

53:37.738 --> 53:38.739
Just temporary.

53:40.004 --> 53:41.206
Grab a gun.

53:49.571 --> 53:50.838
I love the way I look.

53:52.539 --> 53:53.639
(classical music)

54:22.671 --> 54:23.672
Help!

54:31.671 --> 54:32.672
Help me!

54:34.338 --> 54:35.339
Help!

54:38.471 --> 54:39.839
(serene opera singing)

55:31.704 --> 55:32.704
You see this?

55:33.937 --> 55:36.506
