55:41.338 --> 55:42.339
that's my hell.

55:43.938 --> 55:45.303
For the time,

55:45.305 --> 55:46.306
yours too.

55:46.937 --> 55:47.938
See,

55:48.472 --> 55:50.305
the crime that got me here,

55:51.371 --> 55:52.871
well, that was cowardice

55:53.371 --> 55:54.437
Didn't even get me to

55:54.439 --> 55:56.373
the top of the first circle.

55:57.737 --> 55:58.771
Now see I'm...

55:59.705 --> 56:01.639
I'm just outside the gates,
right there.

56:03.472 --> 56:04.472
So,

56:04.904 --> 56:05.905
every day,

56:07.771 --> 56:09.539
I have to pay for my sins.

56:10.704 --> 56:11.705
My family

56:12.838 --> 56:14.639
would go on vacation in
New Jersey every summer.

56:16.305 --> 56:17.405
Wild Wood.

56:18.404 --> 56:20.738
My mom, my dad,

56:22.304 --> 56:23.571
and my brother Joey.

56:24.638 --> 56:25.702
See, Joey,

56:25.704 --> 56:27.803
he was two years older than me.

56:27.805 --> 56:28.936
His favorite ride was...

56:28.938 --> 56:30.536
was always the haunted houses.

56:30.538 --> 56:32.239
I'm scared to hell of it,

56:33.504 --> 56:34.602
he would tease me.

56:34.604 --> 56:36.237
Until I eventually agreed

56:36.239 --> 56:37.502
to go on the ride with him.

56:37.504 --> 56:38.535
But even then, I just, I just

56:38.537 --> 56:40.302
still just, I closed my eyes

56:40.304 --> 56:41.672
the entire ride, right.

56:42.738 --> 56:44.502
But the scariest one of them all
was

56:44.504 --> 56:45.905
called the Pit of Doom.

56:46.871 --> 56:47.872
One night,

56:48.471 --> 56:49.738
while we were there,

56:50.004 --> 56:51.206
it burned.

56:52.238 --> 56:54.871
Joey and I were on that ride
when it went down.

56:56.604 --> 56:58.239
Halfway through the ride,

56:59.271 --> 57:00.272
we stopped.

57:02.239 --> 57:03.306
Lights went out.

57:05.470 --> 57:06.804
Smoke was everywhere.

57:07.239 --> 57:08.472
The place it, it...

57:09.470 --> 57:11.471
was engulfed in seconds, really

57:11.870 --> 57:15.206
but a man with a flashlight came
by.

57:16.604 --> 57:17.605
Found us.

57:18.239 --> 57:20.003
He pulled us out of the car.

57:20.005 --> 57:22.536
